</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * So physical education teacher Pamela Altea "placed herself in jeopardy" of 
the vicious beating she received by male gang members because she left her 
school's gate open due to a faulty lock, heh (Feb. 17)? 
</P>
<P>
 That any thinking, responsible person -- much less Altea's colleagues -- would 
