<HEADLINE>
<P>
SERVICES FOR CREACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Memorial services for violinist "Papa" John Creach, who died Tuesday in Los 
Angeles at age 76, will be held at 2:30 p.m. Monday at Angelus Funeral Home, 
3875 S. Crenshaw Blvd., Los Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
 Creach, who played with Jefferson Airplane and Jefferson Starship as well as 
his own band, is survived by his wife, Sylvia (Gretchen) Creach, a brother and 
a sister. 
</P>
