 San Fernando (4-3-1) will play Garfield in a second-round match today. 
</P>
<P>
 South Gate forward Carlos Osorio -- who scored a goal against the Tigers -- 
has been academically ineligible since December. Tiger coaches made inquiries 
about Osorio after being suspicious that he was too old to play. Baseball  
</P>
