summer and should be one of the county's top players. But doubles might 
actually be Foothill's strength. "Our doubles carried us last year and I expect 
them to be pretty strong this year," Claus said. "I expect to win league. But 
after that, I don't know. It's amazing how many good teams there are in Orange 
County now." 
