</P>
<P>
 The hearing is expected to resume today in Orange County Juvenile Court. 
</P>
<P>
 The child has been in protective custody at the shelter for neglected and 
abused children since Feb. 18, six days after his biological parents allegedly 
abducted him from his foster mother's home in Rancho Santa Margarita. 
</P>
