<P>
TEACHER STRIKE DEFIES COURT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Teachers who have worked without a contract since the start of the school year 
defied a judge's order and went on strike Thursday. 
</P>
